     H            Y.
     F** UTLR07B***********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: UTILITY - STAMP LOG (SAVE MENU PASS LOG) *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)                                    *
     F*  SET TO : JW (SRA)                                    *
     F*  DATE   : 10/11/2019                                  *
     F*-------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR07B'
     F*                    PARM           $PGM   10
     F*                    PARM           $COM   10
     F*  IN  $PGM   :  10A : PROGRAM
     F*      $COM   :  10A : COMMENT PASSED FROM CL
     F******************************************************
     FUTLWP07BO   E                    DISK
     FUTLPP07BO   E                    DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $PGM    6
     C                     PARM           $COM   10
      *
     C                     MOVEL#WSID     U1WSID
     C                     MOVEL#USER     U1USER
     C                     MOVEL$PGM      U1PGM     P
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     U1CRDT
     C                     TIME           U1CRTM
     C                     MOVEL$COM      U1COM
     C                     WRITEUTLWP7B1
     C                     WRITEUTLPP7B1
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
